<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='179:187'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='187:197'>　三禮圖集注卷一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='197:217'>　　　　　　　　　　　宋　聶崇義　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='217:247'>　　大裘冕　　　　　衮冕<span class='krp-note'>與后褘衣畫細紐/約明已下皆有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='247:261'>　　鷩冕　　　　　　毳冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='261:276'>　　絺冕　　　　　　𤣥冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='276:291'>　　韋弁服　　　　　皮弁服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='291:307'>　　冠弁服　　　　　三公毳冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='307:333'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-1b' );" name="001-1b" class="pb">[001-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='333:349'>　　上公衮冕　　　　侯伯鷩冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='349:367'>　　子男毳冕　　　　卿大夫𤣥冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='367:381'>　　爵弁　　　　　　皮弁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='381:389'>　　諸侯朝服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='389:412'>周天子吉服有九冕服六弁服三凡九也故司服云王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='412:435'>祀昊天上帝則服大裘而冕祀五帝亦如之享先王則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='435:458'>衮冕享先公饗射則鷩冕祀四望山川則毳冕祭社稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='458:482'>五祀則絺冕祭羣小祀則𤣥冕兵事韋弁服眂朝皮弁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='482:508'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-2a' );" name="001-2a" class="pb">[001-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='508:532'>服凡甸冠弁服又孔疏引弁師掌王之五冕皆𤣥冕朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='532:556'>裏止言𤣥朱而已不言所用之物論語云麻冕禮也盖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='556:581'>以布衣版上𤣥下纁取天地之色其長短廣狭則經𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='581:604'>無文漢禮器制度云冕制皆長尺六寸廣八寸天子已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='604:627'>下皆同董巴輿服志云廣七寸長尺二寸皇氏沈氏以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='627:650'>為諸侯之冕應劭漢官儀云廣七寸長八寸皇氏沈氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='650:673'>以為卿大夫之冕若依此言豈董巴専記諸侯應劭專</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='673:696'>記卿大夫此蓋隨代變易大小不同今依漢禮制度為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='696:722'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-2b' );" name="001-2b" class="pb">[001-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='722:745'>定謂之冕冕者俛也後髙前下有俯俛之形故因名焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='745:768'>盖以在位者失扵驕矜欲令位彌髙而志彌下故制此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='768:791'>冕令貴者下賤者也其服舊説云天子九章據大章而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='791:814'>言其章别分小章章依命數則皆十二為莭上公亦九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='814:837'>章無升龍有降龍其小章章别皆九而已鷩冕毳冕以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='837:860'>下皆然必知有小章者若無小章絺冕三章則孤有四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='860:884'>命六命卿大夫𤣥冕一章卿大夫中則有三命二命一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='884:907'>命天子之卿六命大夫四命明大章中有小章乃可得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='907:933'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-3a' );" name="001-3a" class="pb">[001-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='933:956'>依命數又司馬彪漢書輿服志云明帝永平二年初詔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='956:980'>有司采周官禮記尚書之文制冕皆前圎後方朱裏𤣥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='980:1003'>上前垂四寸後三寸王用白玉珠十二旒三公諸侯青</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1003:1026'>玉七旒卿大夫黒玉五旒皆有前無後此亦漢法耳今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1026:1049'>案三禮經注孔賈疏義并諸家禮圖逐冕下别各明其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1049:1062'>制度則古今沿革事可知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1062:1088'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-4a' );" name="001-4a" class="pb">[001-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
