<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1112:1138'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-4b' );" name="001-4b" class="pb">[001-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1138:1162'>大裘者黒羔裘也其冕無旒亦𤣥表纁裏案鄭志大裘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1162:1186'>之上又有𤣥衣與裘同色但無文彩耳裘下有裳纁色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1186:1210'>朱韍素帶朱裏朱緑終辟佩白玉而𤣥組綬赤舄黒絇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1210:1233'>繶純絇者謂拘屨舄之頭以為行戒繶縫中紃也純縁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1233:1256'>也三者皆黒色大裘已下冕皆前圓後方天子以球玉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1256:1276'>為笏王祀昊天上帝五帝崐崘神州皆服大裘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1276:1302'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '001-5a' );" name="001-5a" class="pb">[001-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
